<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="advise-v">advise <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /əd'vaɪz/    美 /əd'vaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>劝告；建议：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s easy for you to advise, but difficult to take advice from others. 
劝告别人容易，接受别人的劝告就难了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advise sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I advised them to take Bus No. 20, which could take them there directly.
我建议他们乘坐20路公交车，这样他们就能直达那里。</p><footer>2012 北京书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You are advised to book in advance.
建议您提前预订。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advise doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They advised putting off the meeting till next week.
他们建议把会议推迟到下星期。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advise (sb) + that … (should) do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The doctor advised Vera strongly that she (should) take a holiday.
医生强烈建议维拉休假。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It is strongly advised that</strong> the contracts be read through thoroughly. 
强烈建议把合同仔细看一遍。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advise (sb) on sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She advised the government on environmental issues.
她就环境问题给政府提建议。</p></div>

<h3 id="advise-suggest">辨析 advise, suggest</h3>
<p>表示“建议”时，二者意义十分接近。但用法不尽相同。<br />
<strong>advise</strong> 
<strong>suggest</strong> </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>doing sth 
建议做某事</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>that …(should) do sth 
提议…做某事</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[正式用语] 通知</strong></h4>
<p>to officially tell sb sth：</p>
<ul>
<li>advise sb of sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please advise us of any changes in your personal details. 
你的个人资料如有变化，敬请告知。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advise sb + that/wh- 从句:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ll have about one hour to explore the area, and your tour guide will advise you what time you should be back. 
你们将有约一小时的时间在这一区域考察，之后导游会通知你们几点返回。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I regret to advise you that the course is now full.
很遗憾地通知你，这门课程现在已满额。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>adviser / advisor /əd'vaɪzə(r)/ n [C]  </p></div>